document_data.name: Sultlue Vault
document_data.location: [[Waterdeep/City of the Dead|City of the Dead]], [[Waterdeep]]
document_data.mainbody: '''Sultlue Vault''' was a tomb located within the [[Waterdeep/City of the Dead|City of the Dead]] in [[Waterdeep]].
document_data.Location: Sultlue Vault was located in the western section of the City of the Dead.
document_data.Defenses: The tomb was heavily warded with [[magic]].
document_data.Inhabitants: [[Sylsinssath Sultlue]], a [[yuan-ti pureblood]] and prior member of [[House Eselemas]], slumbered within the tomb which he used as a refuge. He was accompanied by a group of [[tainted one]]s and members of the [[Sultlue]] family visited on a regular basis to attend to his needs.
